tid":459664,"uid":92859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T11:21:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打你地籠底用咩吸尿</blockquote><br />\n尿片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好好用<br />\n換果陣一野包哂啲屎尿換塊新就得"},{"pid":"ad372bbbe5e3a2e3e2931f8d8af0bd3df8335174","tid":459664,"uid":92859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T11:26:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本身有一隻龍貓，好想買多隻做伴<br />\n睇過旺角幾間都好貴，又怕黑店<br />\n仲有咩選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 領養可遇不可求</blockquote><br />\n我果隻都係旺角買<br />\n本身上網睇搵過幾個賣家但係唔成事<br />\n最後係旺角一間咁啱見到呢隻衰野夠平（$2xxx）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後叫店員抱出黎睇下就決定左係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過間野啲服務態度真係麻麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f26abaf729165668b82599caa2db4443fbef0744","tid":459664,"uid":93864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T12:39:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本身有一隻龍貓，好想買多隻做伴<br />\n睇過旺角幾間都好貴，又怕黑店<br />\n仲有咩選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 領養可遇不可求</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最出名都應該係多多龍或者旺角樓上鋪果間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己果隻就貪平2千幾係濕9鋪頭買左，唔知係咪基因/品種問題，好輕磅，keep住500g上下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28d7711e7666dc7b1450fa894ada923a6d1e7409","tid":459664,"uid":93864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T12:40:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>本身有一隻龍貓，好想買多隻做伴<br />\n睇過旺角幾間都好貴，又怕黑店<br />\n仲有咩選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 領養可遇不可求</blockquote><br />\n我果隻都係旺角買<br />\n本身上網睇搵過幾個賣家但係唔成事<br />\n最後係旺角一間咁啱見到呢隻衰野夠平（$2xxx）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後叫店員抱出黎睇下就決定左係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過間野啲服務態度真係麻麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nChing你果隻幾重啊？<br />\n做左奴才幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67974f5b038947c51a1aa9170126f0c3075b9984","tid":459664,"uid":82081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T15:27:32.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打可以講下唔同色/品種既價位係幾多?<br />\n同埋係咪要每日餵野食?<br />\n可唔可以比定一堆野食同水佢自己食.?<br />\n因為未必每日照顧到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能2-3日先照顧到佢一次"},{"pid":"5143695ab782682c7def46b4a375531c059f2d80","tid":459664,"uid":92859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T00:03:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>本身有一隻龍貓，好想買多隻做伴<br />\n睇過旺角幾間都好貴，又怕黑店<br />\n仲有咩選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 領養可遇不可求</blockquote><br />\n我果隻都係旺角買<br />\n本身上網睇搵過幾個賣家但係唔成事<br />\n最後係旺角一間咁啱見到呢隻衰野夠平（$2xxx）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後叫店員抱出黎睇下就決定左係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過間野啲服務態度真係麻麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nChing你果隻幾重啊？<br />\n做左奴才幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇磅，不過佢依加比初初黎果陣肥左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"572b85647097d89aa1532bc11c350d12c9aa3d0a","tid":459664,"uid":125665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T00:06:01.000Z","msg":"龍貓親唔親人？同埋會唔會認得主人？"},{"pid":"f155b2f5e85be9ea126d1357f31422365dde6357","tid":459664,"uid":93864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T00:10:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>龍貓親唔親人？同埋會唔會認得主人？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n教得好基本上同狗既智慧差唔多，親唔親人就隻隻都唔同，不過9成龍貓都鐘意r痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cfd0bb060aba03fa4c4c88911288f4949cf7ffc","tid":459664,"uid":92859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T00:11:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇巴打可以講下唔同色/品種既價位係幾多?<br />\n同埋係咪要每日餵野食?<br />\n可唔可以比定一堆野食同水佢自己食.?<br />\n因為未必每日照顧到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能2-3日先照顧到佢一次</blockquote><br />\n最平應該係標準灰同杏色$1500-2000<br />\n其他有紫灰，銀班，黑色白色etc<br />\n價錢由幾千到幾萬都有<br />\n<br />\n不過如果唔可以每日照顧就唔好養啦<br />\n雖然話龍貓識食飽就停<br />\n但你俾太多糧可能會俾佢掉哂落籠底之後食唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋龍貓都好需要人陪，最起碼每日抽少少時間陪佢玩一陣"},{"pid":"e82504dcb72cf8c4e079ef4718f183bee46eb30e","tid":459664,"uid":93864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T00:11:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇巴打可以講下唔同色/品種既價位係幾多?<br />\n同埋係咪要每日餵野食?<br />\n可唔可以比定一堆野食同水佢自己食.?<br />\n因為未必每日照顧到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能2-3日先照顧到佢一次</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2-3日先照顧到一次就唔建議養啦，始終都係寵物<br />\n隔日照顧分分鐘小病變大病"},{"pid":"f7a8837273355103a92366fd40fb24c7a92db3a2","tid":459664,"uid":92859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T00:18:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>龍貓親唔親人？同埋會唔會認得主人？</blockquote><br />\n識認人但唔一定癡人，見到陌生人會哩埋<br />\n<br />\n我果隻去撩佢會走佬，放出黎free run唔理佢又會冤住你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好傲嬌<br />\n<br />\n同埋一聽到膠袋聲就知有野食會發癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e40930177e12a68888a325cc0fa12fcf089f2444","tid":459664,"uid":93864,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T00:20:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/081500_40987f9635a741c81f7411df16a0e0e6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F081500_40987f9635a741c81f7411df16a0e0e6.jpg&h=664b5469&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/081503_da5c947d60b436492bd43054aa8c9a0a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F081503_da5c947d60b436492bd43054aa8c9a0a.jpg&h=bdc0f375&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/081507_b8d85f76cd70587bb1302b1e9a1ad954.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F081507_b8d85f76cd70587bb1302b1e9a1ad954.jpg&h=321f9908&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望有圖多啲人入黎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"449b579b757ad85ec1d51bd58be8bd0ee33981fc","tid":459664,"uid":92859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T01:44:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/081500_40987f9635a741c81f7411df16a0e0e6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F081500_40987f9635a741c81f7411df16a0e0e6.jpg&h=664b5469&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/081503_da5c947d60b436492bd43054aa8c9a0a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F081503_da5c947d60b436492bd43054aa8c9a0a.jpg&h=bdc0f375&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/081507_b8d85f76cd70587bb1302b1e9a1ad954.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F081507_b8d85f76cd70587bb1302b1e9a1ad954.jpg&h=321f9908&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望有圖多啲人入黎討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b15b27abbb26ea3f1948d383d2a8b7c855ea4d3e","tid":459664,"uid":142989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T07:34:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇巴打可以講下唔同色/品種既價位係幾多?<br />\n同埋係咪要每日餵野食?<br />\n可唔可以比定一堆野食同水佢自己食.?<br />\n因為未必每日照顧到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能2-3日先照顧到佢一次</blockquote><br />\n灰色最平<br />\n草我係早晚加比佢<br />\n糧就一日換一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72c05831aecf0701c9b2af531761ba191c487c92","tid":459664,"uid":142989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T07:38:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/29/153750_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F29%2F153750_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=cdb2626a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以前瘦到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbfba944ce4de6782b06f72ce67bc1f556fcf05c","tid":459664,"uid":32061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T13:06:01.000Z","msg":"有無巴絲自己合籠？過程難唔難？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ace3b6c288f3b1e462bbc3762a82c97b2bcf3fd","tid":459664,"uid":72694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T09:07:06.000Z","msg":"有冇人係屋企先養貓後養龍貓?<br />\n可唔可以分享下經驗<br />\n好想養但係驚比隻貓嚇到佢適應唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bf96bff6535793ba48b7c483ab12b044e318da9","tid":459664,"uid":100936,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T21:29:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/05/052815_59892ebbb7c215782699e4aebee2c313.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/t